rf = RandomForestClassifier(featuresCol="features", labelCol="Churn") # or "Promotion"
rf_model = rf.fit(train_data)
predictions = rf_model.transform(test_data)
For Salary (Regression - Q1 only):

Python
from pyspark.ml.regression import RandomForestRegressor
lr = RandomForestRegressor(featuresCol="features", labelCol="Salary")
lr_model = lr.fit(train_data)
salary_predictions = lr_model.transform(test_data)
